V0409_01_00_00_0.text: I'm prepped and primed to Duel you!

V0409_01_00_01_0.text:
I have to be careful.
I know you're tricky with your moves.

V0409_01_00_02_0.text:
You seem sure that you'll win.
Allow me to change your mind.

V0409_01_00_04_1.text: I can't wait to see how you feel the flow!

V0409_01_00_05_0.text: My brother's busy, so I'll face you instead.

V0409_01_00_08_0.text:
I won't let my brothers down!
I will defeat you!

V0409_03_00_00_0.text: It's time I bring this Duel to an end!

V0409_03_00_01_0.text: You must think little of me if you still think you can win.

V0409_03_00_05_0.text:
I'm not worried.
I anticipated this turn of events.

V0409_05_00_00_0.text: No matter how hurt I get, I'll win with this draw!

V0409_07_09_00_0.text: I flip over my Set card!

V0409_11_01_00_0.text: I summon a monster in Defense Position!

V0409_11_08_01_0.text:
I build the Overlay Network!
I Xyz Summon!

V0409_16_00_01_0.text: You have nothing to protect you!

V0409_21_00_00_0.text: If you don't do something, you're gonna lose!

V0409_21_00_01_0.text: You don't know when to give up.

V0409_21_00_04_0.text: This doesn't look good for me...

V0409_21_00_05_1.text: I can still make a comeback, so you better watch out!

V0409_28_00_00_0.text: It's a good thing I didn't take you lightly.

V0409_28_00_03_0.text:
I fight for my family.
That's why I'll never lose!

V0409_28_00_04_0.text:
Yuma...
You're the only true friend I have...

V0409_28_00_05_0.text: Since you've mastered your Number, I knew you'd be tough.

V0409_28_00_06_0.text:
We're brothers.
We shouldn't be fighting each other.

V0409_28_00_07_0.text: Quinton, this is the power of my Chronomaly Deck!

V0409_28_00_08_0.text: When we're together, my brothers and I can't be beat!

V0409_29_00_00_0.text:
You have a lot of skill.
No wonder you defeated me.

V0409_29_00_01_0.text: When we meet again, the outcome'll be different!

V0409_29_00_02_0.text: How were you able to overcome the power of my crest?

V0409_29_00_03_0.text: I can't give up, even if it costs me everything.

V0409_29_00_04_0.text: By teaming with Astral, you've grown a lot stronger, Yuma.

V0409_29_00_05_0.text:
Ouch...
That's going too far, Brother.

V0409_29_00_06_0.text: You've always been the best among us, Brother.

V0409_29_00_07_0.text: I've never seen anyone play monsters like that before!

V0409_33_00_00_0.text: I'll show you what I can really do!

V0409_33_00_01_0.text: Your overconfidence is gonna cost you!

V0409_30_00_00_0.text: We shouldn't be fighting each other.

V0409_30_00_01_0.text: Your Dueling is full of surprises.

V0409_30_00_02_0.text: Did you master every possible way to annoy me?

V0409_34_00_00_0.text:
I won't accept your surrender.
Because I want to defeat you!

V0409_34_00_01_0.text: If you think your way's right, prove it!

V0409_34_00_02_0.text: Thank you for your kind words.

V0409_34_00_03_0.text: I found a tiny flaw in your combo!

V0409_34_00_07_0.text: I'm glad to have you as my friend.

V0409_34_00_08_0.text: Chronomaly artifacts prove that another dimension exists!

V0409_34_00_09_0.text: Artifacts of the past created hope for the future!

V0409_35_00_00_0.text: Time to put my Chronomaly Deck into action!

V0409_36_00_01_0.text: I leave the rest to you!

V0409_36_00_02_0.text:
Sorry...
I let them outplay me.

V0409_36_00_03_0.text: Yuma, I know your cards will lead us to victory!

V0409_36_00_04_0.text: Since we're a team, I'll share my power with you!

V0409_36_00_05_0.text:
I'm here to protect you.
To my very last LP!

V0409_36_00_06_0.text: Everything's set up for you to win, Brother.

V0409_36_00_08_0.text:
Argh...
Brother, should we change our strategy?

V0409_36_00_09_0.text: You picked the wrong family to mess with!

V0409_08_00_00_0.text: I activate Rank-Up-Magic Argent Chaos Force!

V0409_08_00_01_0.text: Argent Chaos Force's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0409_08_00_01_1.text: I add this card to my hand!

V0409_08_00_02_0.text: I play the Continuous Spell, Chronomaly Pyramid Eye Tablet!

V0409_08_00_02_1.text: The Chronomaly monsters on my field gain extra ATK!

V0409_08_00_03_0.text: I activate the Spell Card, Chronomaly Technology!

V0409_08_00_03_1.text: I look at two cards in my deck and add one to my hand!

V0409_08_00_04_0.text: I activate the Field Spell, Chronomaly City Babylon!

V0409_08_00_05_0.text: I activate Chronomaly City Babylon's effect!

V0409_08_00_05_1.text: I banish a Chronomaly from my Graveyard to revive another!

V0409_08_00_06_0.text: I play my Continuous Spell, Chronomaly Temple - Trilithon!

V0409_08_00_07_0.text: I activate Chronomaly Temple - Trilithon's effect!

V0409_08_00_07_1.text: I pay my LP to summon a Chronomaly monster from my hand!

V0409_08_00_08_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Stonehenge Methods!

V0409_08_00_08_1.text: When my Chronomaly is destroyed, I can summon another!

V0409_08_00_09_0.text: I activate the Continuous Trap, Number Wall!

V0409_08_00_09_1.text: Number Wall's effect protects my Numbers!

V0409_08_00_10_0.text:
I activate my Trap!
Chronomaly Esperanza Glyph!

V0409_08_00_10_1.text: I summon two Chronomaly monsters and use them to Xyz Summon!

V0409_09_00_00_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Machu Mech's effect!

V0409_09_00_01_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Chateau Huyuk's effect!

V0409_09_00_01_1.text: Your monster's ATK drop to 0 until the end of the turn!

V0409_09_00_02_0.text: I Tribute my Chronomaly to activate Chateau Huyuk's effect!

V0409_09_00_02_1.text: Your monster's ATK changed, so it's destroyed!

V0409_09_00_03_1.text: When it's Xyz Summoned, it equips a Number in my Graveyard!

V0409_09_00_04_1.text: It uses 1 Overlay Unit to cut your LP in half!

V0409_09_00_05_1.text: It can equip one of your monsters once per turn!

V0409_09_00_06_0.text: I use 3 Overlay Units to activate Chaos Atlandis's effect!

V0409_09_00_06_1.text: I get rid of its equipped Numbers to make your LP equal 100!

V0409_09_00_07_0.text: Vimana targets a monster on the field and in the Graveyard!

V0409_09_00_07_1.text: The first gains ATK, and the other becomes an Overlay Unit!

V0409_09_00_08_0.text:
That won't work!
I activate Chronomaly Vimana's effect!

V0409_09_00_08_1.text: By using 2 Overlay Units, I negate your monster's effect!

V0409_09_00_09_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to play Crystal Chrononaut's effect!

V0409_09_00_09_1.text: When it battles, you take the damage I would've taken!

V0409_09_00_10_0.text: By summoning this Sphinx, I can revive a Level 5 Chronomaly!

V0409_09_00_11_1.text: I Tribute a Chronomaly to lower your monster's ATK!

V0409_09_00_12_0.text: I activate Crystal Skull's effect from my hand!

V0409_09_00_12_1.text: I add a Chronomaly from my deck or Graveyard to my hand!

V0409_09_00_13_0.text: Crystal Bones summoned itself, so I can Special Summon a Chronomaly!

V0409_09_00_14_0.text: I activate Chronomaly Colossal Head's effect!

V0409_09_00_14_1.text: I banish it from my Grave to switch a monster to defense!

V0409_09_00_15_1.text: It raises my Chronomaly monsters' Levels by 1!

V0409_09_00_16_0.text: Gordian Knot Special Summons a Chronomaly from my hand!

V0409_09_00_16_1.text: And it becomes the same Level as the monster it summoned!

V0409_09_00_17_1.text: Once per turn, it can change my Chronomaly's Level to 6!

V0409_09_00_18_1.text: I send a Chronomaly to the Grave to lower a monster's ATK!

V0409_09_00_19_0.text: When Nebra Disk is summoned, I can activate its effect!

V0409_09_00_19_1.text: I add a Chronomaly card in my deck to my hand!

V0409_09_00_20_0.text: Nebra Disk's effect activates from the Graveyard!

V0409_09_00_20_1.text: It resurrects when I only have Chronomaly monsters in play!

V0409_09_00_21_1.text: I tribute it to Special Summon a Chronomaly from my deck!

V0409_09_00_22_0.text: I activate Magella Globe's effect from my Graveyard!

V0409_09_00_22_1.text: I can retrieve it by banishing a Chronomaly in my Graveyard!

V0409_09_00_23_0.text: Acambaro Figures's effect activates from my Graveyard!

V0409_09_00_23_1.text: I pay my LP to Special Summon it from my Graveyard!

V0409_09_00_24_0.text: I use 1 Overlay Unit to activate Shark Drake's effect!

V0409_09_00_24_1.text: It revives your monster - but with fewer ATK!

V0409_09_00_24_2.text: Then it can battle your monster again!

V0409_37_00_00_1.text:
Transcend time and space to emerge in this world!
Number C6!

V0409_37_00_01_0.text: This denizen of the deep is thirsting for a feeding frenzy!

V0409_19_00_13_0.text: I attack with my Gordian Knot!

V0409_19_00_24_0.text:
Shark Drake!
Sink your teeth to the bone!
